            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收挫175點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收報7.2899，較上日官方收盤價跌175點，較上日夜盤收盤跌179點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14687233-%e5%9c%a8%e5%b2%b8%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3%e5%85%8c%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%94%b6%e6%8c%ab175%e9%bb%9e",
